Amount of oak wood required for one dresser

description: A chair produced by Elm Furniture yields a profit of \param{ProfitChair}, while every dresser yields a \param{ProfitDresser} profit. Each week, \param{TotalStain} gallons of stain and \param{TotalOak} lengths of oak wood are available. Each chair requires \param{StainPerChair} gallons of stain and \param{OakPerChair} lengths of oak wood, while each dresser requires \param{StainPerDresser} gallons of stain and \param{OakPerDresser} lengths of oak wood. Determine the maximum profit.
